[{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0070","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0070.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1875","title":"Joomla! 房产组件 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! com_properties 组件 3.1.22-03 版本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 index.php 的 controller 参数传入目录遍历序列（..）读取服务器任意文件，甚至可能导致其他未明确的影响。该漏洞属于路径遍历类漏洞（CWE-22），CVSS 评分 7.5（高危），攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，通过构造包含目录遍历序列的 controller 参数即可读取服务器敏感文件。该漏洞影响 Joomla! 使用 com_properties 3.1.22-03 组件的站点，攻击者可利用该漏洞读取服务器敏感配置文件、源代码等敏感信息，进而导致信息泄露或进一步攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1875"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-12T11:46:12.643","updated":"2026-06-16T23:19:30.480","remediation":"立即升级 Joomla! 的 Real Estate Property (com_properties) 组件至已修复目录穿越问题的版本（3.1.22-03 之后的官方更新版）；若官方暂无可升级版本，应在后台扩展管理中停用或卸载该组件。作为临时缓解，可在 Web 服务器（如 Apache/Nginx）或 WAF 上添加规则，拦截对 index.php 的 controller 参数中包含\"../\"或\"..\"的请求，并限制 PHP 仅允许包含组件白名单目录内的文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/39074","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11851","http://www.osvdb.org/63143","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/38912","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57110","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11851","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1875.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-1875.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1875.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1875.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-1875-1827.yaml","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/CVE-2010-1875.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1875_49.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-1875-1829.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/20/Artifact/Report.csv","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1875_41.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24b6c514a7b18b3a83429b0eaa19c9cb61a02fb8/cves/2010/1xxx/CVE-2010-1875.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0070.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0071","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0071.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1878","title":"Joomla! Component OrgChart 1.0.0 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 OrgChart（com_orgchart）组件 1.0.0 版本存在目录遍历（本地文件包含）漏洞，属于 CWE-22 路径遍历类缺陷。该组件在处理 index.php 的 controller 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤与规范化，攻击者可在参数中插入\"..\"（点点）序列穿越目录层级。未经身份认证的远程攻击者只需向目标站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求（如将 controller 参数设置为包含 ../ 的路径），即可读取服务器上任意文件，包括配置文件、源码及敏感系统文件，从而导致信息泄露。该漏洞影响所有运行 OrgChart 1.0.0 组件的 Joomla! 站点，CVSS 评分为 7.5，危害等级为高。利用方式简单，仅需构造包含目录遍历序列的 URL 即可，无需认证或特殊权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1878"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-12T11:46:12.737","updated":"2026-06-16T23:19:30.810","remediation":"建议立即卸载或禁用 Joomla! OrgChart 组件 (com_orgchart) 1.0.0，升级至官方修复版本（若有）或替换为同类安全组件。临时缓解：在 Web 应用防火墙 (WAF) 配置规则拦截 controller 参数中的 `../` 等目录遍历载荷，同时限制 PHP open_basedir 目录防止跨目录读取敏感文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlaorgchart-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12317","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39606","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58031","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12317","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1878.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-1878.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1878.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1878.js","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-1878-1834.yaml","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/cve-2010-1878-1833.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1878_9.yaml","https://github.com/patrickmpalmer/exploit-prediction-calculator/blob/a048424e68e6b5ea7f4d32bf29dddd4eda342b01/data_gathering/data/exploited_cves.csv","https://github.com/w4n95/vuls-data-raw-exploit-inthewild/blob/2c8c2568a21a9cc77244882f65c37bca47d71613/2010/CVE-2010-1878.json","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-1878_4.yaml","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dirtra.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0071.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0068","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0068.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1858","title":"Joomla! SMEStorage 组件目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 SMEStorage 组件（com_smestorage）1.1 之前版本存在目录遍历漏洞。该漏洞源于组件对 index.php 的 controller 参数未充分过滤路径遍历序列（如 ../），远程未认证攻击者可构造包含目录遍历序列的请求（如 index.php?option=com_smestorage&controller=../../../../etc/passwd）读取服务器上的任意文件，包括系统敏感文件、配置文件及数据库凭据等，从而导致敏感信息泄露。漏洞对应 CWE-22（路径遍历），CVSS v2 评分 5.0（中危），攻击向量为网络、无需认证、仅影响机密性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1858"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-07","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"将 Joomla! 的 SMEStorage 组件（com_smestorage）升级至 1.1 或更高版本以彻底修复该漏洞。若暂时无法升级，应在服务端对 controller 等用户可控参数进行严格白名单校验，拒绝包含 ../、..\\ 或空字节等路径遍历字符的输入，并使用规范化后的绝对路径进行文件访问限制，避免直接将用户输入拼接到文件路径中。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1003-exploits/joomlasmestorage-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39071","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11853","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/38911","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57108","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2010-1858","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1858.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0068.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0061","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0061.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1714","title":"Joomla 组件 Arcade Games 1.0 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! Arcade Games 组件 1.0 版本存在目录遍历漏洞，攻击者可通过 index.php 的 controller 参数传入目录遍历序列（../）读取服务器任意文件。该漏洞影响 Joomla! 使用 com_arcadegames 1.0 组件的站点，远程未授权攻击者可直接通过构造恶意 controller 参数实现任意文件读取，CVSS 评分 5.0（中危），属于 CWE-22 路径遍历类漏洞。攻击者无需认证即可利用 controller 参数中的目录遍历序列读取服务器敏感文件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1714"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-04T16:00:36.027","updated":"2026-06-16T23:19:10.747","remediation":"建议将 Arcade Games (com_arcadegames) 组件升级至官方修复目录遍历问题的版本；若该组件已停止维护，应在 Joomla 后台扩展管理中直接卸载或禁用该组件。临时缓解措施：在 Web 服务器（如 Apache/Nginx）层部署过滤规则，拦截 index.php 的 controller 参数中包含 ../ 或 .. 的请求，或使用 ModSecurity 等 WAF 规则阻止路径穿越字符，并限制 Web 目录文件读取权限以减小信息泄露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlaarcadegames-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39413","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12168","http://www.osvdb.org/63660","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/0860","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57683","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12168","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1714.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2010/POC-AVE-2010-0061.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0061.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0062","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0062.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1715","title":"Joomla! Online Exam 组件本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Online Examination（又名 Online Exam，组件名 com_onlineexam）1.5.0 版本存在目录穿越（本地文件包含）漏洞。其根源在于组件在处理 index.php 的 controller 参数时未对用户输入进行充分的路径过滤与规范化，导致攻击者可插入\"../\"等特殊路径序列。未经身份认证的远程攻击者只需向目标站点发送特制请求，即可读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、密码哈希等敏感信息），造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响所有安装了 com_onlineexam 1.5.0 组件的 Joomla! 网站，利用方式简单，仅需网络访问其 Web 前端即可发起攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1715"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-04T16:00:36.073","updated":"2026-06-16T23:19:10.863","remediation":"建议升级至 Joomla! Online Exam 组件 1.5.1 或更高版本的版本，该版本修复了目录遍历漏洞。如无法立即升级，请在防火墙中阻止传入的 HTTP 请求中包含 '..' 等目录穿越字符串作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlaonlineexam-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39414","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12174","http://www.osvdb.org/63659","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57677","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12174","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1715.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-1715.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1715.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c7743