719","title":"Joomla! MT Fire Eagle 组件 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 系统中 MT Fire Eagle 组件 v1.2 存在目录遍历漏洞。攻击者可通过向 index.php 发送包含 '..' (点点) 路径的 controller 参数，绕过验证访问服务器上的任意文件。攻击者无需身份验证即可远程控制目标服务器，存在读取敏感文件、执行代码等风险。该漏洞影响 Joomla! 系统用户，CVSS 评分 6.8，属于中危等级。补丁建议升级到最新版本并修复路径验证漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1719"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-04T16:00:36.200","updated":"2026-06-16T23:19:11.330","remediation":"建议立即卸载或禁用 Joomla! MT Fire Eagle 1.2 组件，或升级至官方修复版本（如有）。临时缓解措施：在 Web 应用防火墙配置规则拦截 controller 参数中的目录遍历序列（../），并限制 Web 服务器进程对敏感目录的读取权限。建议升级 Joomla 核心及所有组件至最新安全版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/63806","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlamtfireeagle-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39470","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12233","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39509","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57850","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12233","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1719.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-1719.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1719.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1719.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-1719-1799.yaml","https://github.com/gongzeq/VAPT3/blob/3576a7accf5cbadc8e64924d6ff48393db379ea7/secbot/resource/poc/cve/cve-2010-1719-1797.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1719_9.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-1719-1797.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Oct/09/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/gongzeq/VAPT3/blob/3576a7accf5cbadc8e64924d6ff48393db379ea7/secbot/resource/poc/cve/cve-2010-1719-1798.yaml","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/f2d12f176efdb99f18928b2678d34b7fa4f530f8/content/CVE-2010-1719.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0065.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0066","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0066.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1722","title":"Joomla! Online Market 2.x 组件目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! Online Market (com_market) 组件 2.x 版本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 index.php 的 controller 参数传入 ../ 目录遍历序列，读取服务器任意文件并可能导致其他未知影响。该漏洞影响 Joomla! Online Market 组件 2.x 版本，CVSS 评分 6.8，属中危漏洞。攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，通过构造包含目录遍历序列的 controller 参数实现任意文件读取，可能导致敏感文件泄露进而进一步攻击服务器。攻击者只需构造恶意 URL 访问 index.php?option=com_market&controller=../../../../etc/passwd%00 等路径即可实现利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1722"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-04T16:00:36.293","updated":"2026-06-16T23:19:11.683","remediation":"建议立即在 Joomla! 后台扩展管理器中卸载或禁用存在漏洞的 Online Market (com_market) 2.x 组件；若业务必须保留该组件，应升级到已修复 controller 参数过滤的版本，并在组件代码中对 controller 参数做白名单校验，仅允许字母数字，拦截包含 ../ 及空字节的序列；同时升级 PHP 至修复空字节截断的 5.3.4 及以上版本，并在站点根目录 .htaccess 中限制对 index.php?option=com_market 的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlaonlinemarket-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39409","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12177","http://www.osvdb.org/63671","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57674","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12177","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1722.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef