ublished":"2010-05-03T13:51:53.247","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:48.123","remediation":"升级 Joomla! 到 3.10.13 及以上版本或 4.x 系列，或移除已废弃的 NoticeBoard 组件。进一步的安全措施包括应用安全补丁、限制文件权限、禁用目录遍历功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlnoticeboard-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39600","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12427","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39742","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/1007","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58176"],"poc_urls":["http://localhost/index.php?option=com_noticeboard&controller=../../../../../../../../../etc/passwd%00"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0059.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0060","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0060.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1659","title":"Joomla! Ultimate Portfolio 组件 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! CMS 旗下 Ultimate Portfolio 1.0 组件存在目录遍历漏洞，攻击者可通过向 index.php 发起请求时在控制器参数中嵌入 '..' 路径穿越序列，绕过验证访问服务器上任意文件。该漏洞影响 Joomla! 用户，导致敏感信息泄露。漏洞因可读取文件而具备安全风险，CVSS 评分 5.0，等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1659"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-03T13:51:53.277","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:48.237","remediation":"立即卸载或禁用 Joomla! Ultimate Portfolio 组件（com_ultimateportfolio）1.0 版本，该组件已停止维护无官方补丁。若必须保留，请在 index.php 中对 controller 参数实施严格白名单校验，仅允许字母数字下划线，拦截包含 ../ 或 ..\\ 的请求。同时在 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）配置规则阻断路径遍历载荷，并限制 PHP open_basedir 目录防止跨目录读取敏感文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlaultimateportfolio-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12426","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39739","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/1008","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58177","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12426","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-te