martsite，请确保使用受信任的来源安装，并定期更新至最新安全版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T11:59:04.620207017+00:00","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlasmartsite-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39592","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12428","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39740","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/1006","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58175"],"poc_urls":["http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12428"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0058.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0055","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0055.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1603","title":"Joomla! 组件 ZiMBCore 0.1 - 局部文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 ZiMBCore（com_zimbcore）组件 0.1 版本存在目录穿越漏洞。该组件在处理 index.php 的 controller 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤，远程攻击者可构造包含 `..`（点点）序列的恶意请求，绕过路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、敏感源码等）。由于 Joomla! 通常部署于公开 Web 服务器，任何未经过身份认证的远程用户只要能访问目标站点即可发起攻击，无需特殊权限或前置条件，攻击门槛较低。利用方式简单，仅需向 index.php 发送带有恶意 controller 参数的 HTTP 请求即可触发，除任意文件读取外还可能造成其他未明确的影响，属于高危信息泄露类漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1603"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-29T17:30:00.683","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:41.490","remediation":"建议立即卸载或禁用 Joomla! ZiMBCore 0.1 组件，或升级至 ZiMB Manager 系列最新版本。临时缓解措施：在 Web 应用防火墙层面拦截包含目录遍历序列（../）的 controller 参数请求，或在 Joomla 后台禁用 com_zimbcore 组件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlazimbmanager-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12284","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39546","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/0931","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12284","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1603.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1603.md","https://github.com/projectdiscove